  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dc0 \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba\u0daf\u0db8 \u0da9\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dbb\u0dca 5900 - 8700\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The cost of a night in the hotel where Gotha is said to be between 5900 - 8700 dollars.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Maldives media reports that Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa stayed at the famous Waldorf Astoria Ithaafushi hotel during his stay in Maldives. This hotel chain belongs to a well-known businessman, Mohammad Ali Jana.",
        "He is close to Maldives Foreign Minister Abdullah Shahid. The Maldivian staff of this hotel chain have confirmed that the President is staying at the hotel.",
        "However, the staff expressed displeasure about the President staying there.",
        "The cost of spending a night in this hotel chain is between US$ 5,903 and US$ 8,760. The Government of Maldives has not yet issued a statement in this regard."
      ],
